# setuptools-pipfile

Dependency management via Pipfile

[![CI](https://github.com/asyncon/setuptools-pipfile/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/asyncon/setuptools-pipfile/actions/workflows/ci.yml)
